<tr id="L56"><td><a href="#L56">56</a></td><td>COCHRANE [OC]:  Hello! Hello!</td></tr>

<tr id="L57"><td><a href="#L57">57</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: A figure in an orange jumpsuit waves and runs towards them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L58"><td><a href="#L58">58</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Fascinating.</td></tr>

<tr id="L59"><td><a href="#L59">59</a></td><td>KIRK:  Bones, get a physiological reading on that, whatever it is.</td></tr>

