<tr id="L64"><td><a href="#L64">64</a></td><td>COCHRANE:  The F? Well, it doesn't matter. I'm Cochrane. I've been marooned here who knows how long. If you only knew how good it is to see you. And a woman. A beautiful one at that.</td></tr>

<tr id="L65"><td><a href="#L65">65</a></td><td>KIRK:  I'm Captain James T. Kirk, commanding the starship Enterprise. (they shake hands) This is my first officer Mister Spock.</td></tr>

